offers.name: BerbaPrime
offers.html_description:
High-strength berberine HCL 97% (1500mg) offers a natural way to support your health every day
Supports a healthy metabolism
Supports healthy cholesterol levels
Supports healthy blood sugar levels

Used in traditional Chinese medicine for thousands of years, hundreds of studies have now revealed the extraordinary health benefits of berberine.

This entirely natural, plant-based alkaloid is so powerful that scientists believe it could help protect against - and even help treat - chronic health conditions like high cholesterol, metabolic syndrome, diabetes and heart disease - the leading cause of death worldwide.

Berberine can help control blood sugar by activating an enzyme called AMPK (AMPK-activated protein kinase).

AMPK increases the movement of glucose (sugar) from your blood into your cells, increases the breakdown of that glucose into energy (a process called glycolysis) and slows production of glucose in the liver.

By controlling how your body processes glucose and improving insulin resistance, berberine can help support healthy blood sugar levels.

In fact, studies have shown that berberine can significantly lower blood sugar levels in people with type 2 diabetes1 and may even be as effective as some diabetes medications2
